### NuGet Product(s) Involved

NuGet SDK

### The Elevator Pitch

We are creating a new SDK that partners will consume and will have consistent changes to the package. We want partners to be able to consume the latest version of the SDK and always build with the latest be being able to use wildcards such as 

```JSON
{
  "msbuild-sdks": {
    "Microsoft.Build.Traversal": "3.0.2",
    "Microsoft.Build.NoTargets": "2.0.1",
    "Microsoft.Substrate.Euclid.Sdk.Python": "1.0.*"
  },
  "sdk": {
  "version": "3.1.416"
  }
}
```
